Following the final battle of Tremor VIII, documentation of the aftermath was
collected.&nbsp; These photos are of the Kodiak piloted by Major Giordano.<br>
His heroic stand against overwhelming armored forces has stood as testament to
the 'Corps.&nbsp; Following this battle, demand for Kodiak mecha reached an all
time high amongst commanders of the Space Corps.&nbsp;
<hr>
<table border="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">Showing the wreckage of the Kodiak
      as it was found. The right arm, left hand, and most of the left tthigh have
      been completely destroyed. </td>
    <td><a href="images/kodiakpov/afteraction/downhard.jpg"><img border="0" src="images/kodiakpov/small/downhard_small.jpg" width="100" height="75"></a></td>
  </tr>
