  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">The left thigh was the first major
      damage taken by the Kodiak according to eye witnesses and recovered
      telemetry.&nbsp; Witnesses have stated that Major Giordano managed to
      continue to pilot&nbsp; the mecha, balancing it on one foot.&nbsp; The
      Kodiak's large, stable footprint allowed it to remain erect.</td>
    <td><a href="images/kodiakpov/afteraction/blownhip.jpg"><img border="0" src="images/kodiakpov/small/blownhip_small.jpg" width="100" height="75"></a></td>
  </tr>
