  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">The loss of the right ankle
      finally brought the Kodiak down, but not before it had destroyed a large
      percentage of the 4 platoons of armor that had been advancing on firebase
      Eta.</td>
    <td><a href="images/kodiakpov/afteraction/ankle.jpg"><img border="0" src="images/kodiakpov/small/ankle_small.jpg" width="100" height="75"></a></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left" colspan="2">
      <hr>
 </td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">The shoulder mounted missle pod
      was found to be empty, but in targeting mode, lending credence to the
      account from witnesses that the pod never stopped firing.&nbsp; From damage
      to enemy armor, the SmartStick pod scored on 80% of it's shots; a
      remarkable achievement considering the battle conditions.&nbsp; Later
      simulations and exercises duplicating the conditions at&nbsp; Tremor VIII
      have never reached such a high level of accuracy.&nbsp; For bravery, Major
      Giordano was posthumously awarded the Star Heart (the highest decoration
      available).</td>
